                            <comment id="156965" author="yong.fan" created="Mon, 27 Jun 2016 05:43:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The test_86 reformats the OST1 device, it only checks whether the reformat works or not, but it does not reformat the MGS (or write conf) as to after reformatting the OST1, it cannot mount to the MGS, so if the subsequent tests do not reformat the system, then will get failure.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
